--- !u!114 &390065123
MonoBehaviour:
  m_ObjectHideFlags: 0
  m_CorrespondingSourceObject: {fileID: 0}
  m_PrefabInstance: {fileID: 0}
  m_PrefabAsset: {fileID: 0}
  m_GameObject: {fileID: 390065121}
  m_Enabled: 1
  m_EditorHideFlags: 0
  m_Script: {fileID: 11500000, guid: f4688fdb7df04437aeb418b961361dc5, type: 3}
  m_Name: 
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: Unity.TextMeshPro::TMPro.TextMeshProUGUI
  m_Material: {fileID: 0}
  m_Color: {r: 1, g: 1, b: 1, a: 1}
  m_RaycastTarget: 1
  m_RaycastPadding: {x: 0, y: 0, z: 0, w: 0}
  m_Maskable: 1
  m_OnCullStateChanged:
    m_PersistentCalls:
      m_Calls: []
  m_text: "<size=120%><b><color=#FFD700>HOW TO PLAY: DICES </color></b></size>\r\n\r\nYour
    goal is simple: Roll three dice and beat the Dealer's total score. But beware
    the House rules!\r\n\r\n<b><color=#00FFFF>THE RULES:</color></b>\r\n\u2022 The
    Dealer rolls his 3 dice first. His score is locked on the table.\r\n\u2022 Choose
    your wager and roll your own 3 dice.\r\n\u2022 If your total sum is <b>HIGHER</b>,
    you <color=#00FF00><b>WIN (x2 Payout)</b></color>.\r\n\u2022 If you roll the
    exact same sum, it's a <b>TIE (Push)</b>. Your bet is safely returned to you.\r\n\u2022
    If your total sum is <b>LOWER</b>, you <color=#FF4444><b>LOSE</b></color> your
    bet.\r\n\r\n<b><color=#FFCC00>SPECIAL EVENTS:</color></b>\r\n\u2022 <b>TRIPLE
    WIN:</b> If you manage to beat the Dealer while rolling 3 identical numbers (e.g.
    <i>4 - 4 - 4</i>), you score a massive <color=#FFD700><b>x10 PAYOUT!</b></color>\r\n\u2022
    <b>DEALER'S CURSE:</b>If the Dealer rolls a perfect 18 (<i>6 - 6 - 6</i>), he
    instantly wins the round and takes your money without giving you a chance to
    roll.\r\n\r\n<i><size=80%>Note: Every play costs 3 Energy.</size></i>\r\n"
