      m_Calls: []
  m_text: "<size=120%><b><color=#FFD700>HOW TO PLAY: SLOT MACHINE</color></b></size>\r\nSpin
    the reels and match symbols to win big.\r\n<b><color=#00FFFF>THE RULES:</color></b>\r\n\u2022
    Set your bet using the chip buttons or the input field.\r\n\u2022 Choose your
    spin multiplier: <b>x1, x2 or x3</b> to scale both cost and reward.\r\n\u2022
    Press <b>SPIN</b>. Match 2 or 3 symbols on the reels to win..\r\n<b><color=#FFCC00>SYMBOL
    PAYOUTS (per 1 credit bet):</color></b>\r\n<color=#00FFFF>3 Matches:</color>\r\n
    Diamond  \u2192  <color=#FFD700><b>x100</b></color>  |  Seven    \u2192  <color=#FFD700><b>x50</b></color> 
    |  Horseshoe \u2192  <b>x20</b>  |  Coin      \u2192  <b>x10</b>\r\n Clover   
    \u2192  <b>x25</b>    |  Grapes    \u2192  <b>x2</b>   |  Orange    \u2192  <b>x1.5</b> 
    |  Cherry    \u2192  <b>x1</b>\r\n<color=#00FFFF>2 Matches:</color>\r\n Diamond
    \u2192 <b>x10</b> | Seven \u2192 <b>x5</b>\r\n Horseshoe \u2192 <b>x2</b> | Coin
    \u2192 <b>x1</b> | Cherry \u2192 <b>x0.5</b>\r\n<b><color=#FFCC00>SPECIAL SYMBOLS:</color></b>\r\n\u2022
    <b>WILD (Clover):</b> Substitutes for any symbol to create the best possible
    winning combination.\r\n\u2022 <b>SCATTER (Coin): 2 Coins</b> \u2192 <color=#00FFFF><b>+3
    Free Spins!</color> 3 Coins</b> \u2192 <color=#00FFFF><b>+10 Free Spins!</b></color>\r\n\u2022
    <b>JACKPOT:</b> Land <b>3 Diamonds</b> to claim the <color=#FFD700><b>Progressive
    Jackpot Pool</b></color> on top of your winnings!\r\n\u2022 Every losing spin
    feeds <b>50%</b> of the bet into the Jackpot Pool.\r\n\r\n<i><size=80%>Note:
    Every spin costs 2 Energy (x multiplier).</size></i>\r\n"
