  m_Maskable: 1
  m_OnCullStateChanged:
    m_PersistentCalls:
      m_Calls: []
  m_text: "<size=120%><b><color=#FFD700>HOW TO PLAY: HIGHER / LOWER </color></b></size>\r\n\r\nYour
    goal is simple: Predict whether the next card drawn from the deck will be Higher
    or Lower than the current one on the table.\r\n\r\n<b><color=#00FFFF>THE RULES:</color></b>\r\n\u2022
    Place your bet and click <b>ROLL</b> to reveal your first card.\r\n\u2022 Decide
    and click if the next card will be <color=#00FF00><b>HIGHER</b></color> or <color=#FF4444><b>LOWER</b></color>.\r\n\u2022
    Card values start from <b>2</b> (the lowest) up to <b>Ace</b> (the highest).\r\n\u2022
    If your guess is correct, you start a winning <b>Streak</b>!\r\n\r\n<b><color=#FFCC00>SPECIAL
    EVENTS:</color></b>\r\n\u2022 <b>THE STREAK:</b> With every correct guess, your
    potential payout multiplies! You can <color=#FFD700><b>CASH OUT</b></color> at
    any time to secure your winnings. But if you guess wrong, you lose it all!\r\n\u2022
    <b>TIE (PUSH):</b> If the values are identical on your very first guess, your
    bet is safely returned. However, a Tie during an active Streak breaks it, and
    you <color=#FF4444><b>LOSE</b></color> the pot!\r\n\r\n<i><size=80%>Note: Every
    play costs 4 Energy.</size></i>"
  m_isRightToLeft: 0
  m_fontAsset: {fileID: 11400000, guid: c579a803aac6cb24184fb3cb064f1215, type: 2}
